   "source": [
    "#Image of our original text file\n",
    "#This text file contains some of the ML and Statistics terms and definitions\n",
    "#For simplicity, I have entered only 15-20 terms to test the bot"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
